评论概述: Great deal, natural fiber, very soft, just order up one size
评论详情: Ordinarily for this price you would be lucky to get either a t-shirt or a pair of leggings, so getting both is a good deal, especially for natural fiber, since it seems like everybody is cutting corners these days by making stuff out of polyester. (Yuck. I don't want to be dressed in plastic.) Because of the low price I was somehow expecting it to be cheap quality, but I was wrong.  The first thing that impressed me was how really super soft the t-shirt is. It feels really nice. It's pretty lightweight, and it's 95% cotton, so it will be nice and comfortable in the warm weather. The color is also very pretty. It fits me well, but it should be noted that I did order a size up from my usual size.  I don't like the bottoms quite as well. Although they are also 95% cotton, which I definitely like, I was hoping for a regular pair of leggings, but these are not fitted enough through the upper legs to really call them that in my book. One might say they're fitted stretch trousers, except the fabric is a bit sheer for that, in fact it's a little sheer in general, although I must say quite comfortable.  Overall a very nice natural fiber no frills combo for a very reasonable price.

The TOPONSKY Women Two Piece Workout Outfits Biker Short-Sleeve Long-Pant Sets offer a stylish and comfortable option for active women. The set includes a short-sleeve top and long pants, both made from a breathable and stretchy fabric that ensures ease of movement during workouts. The material is soft against the skin and provides good moisture-wicking properties, keeping you dry during intense exercise sessions.  The design is both trendy and functional, with a snug fit that accentuates your figure while offering support. The biker style of the pants adds a modern touch, and the set is available in various colors, allowing you to choose one that suits your personal style. The outfit is versatile enough to be worn not just for workouts, but also for casual outings or lounging at home.  Overall, the TOPONSKY Women Two Piece Workout Outfits are a great addition to any fitness wardrobe, combining fashion, comfort, and practicality at an affordable price.

This is a cute two piece workout set. It’s fits perfect so it’s true to size. It fits great and is so comfortable.
